I am an occupational
therapist, and also

00:00:09.360 --> 00:00:11.220 align:middle line:90%
the Therapy Director in Dallas.

00:00:11.220 --> 00:00:14.140 align:middle line:84%
I have the clinic
setting that I can

00:00:14.140 --> 00:00:16.540 align:middle line:84%
work in which allows
me to collaborate

00:00:16.540 --> 00:00:18.370 align:middle line:90%
with the other therapists.

00:00:18.370 --> 00:00:21.280 align:middle line:84%
