00:00:27.610 --> 00:00:31.650 align:middle line:84%
It's-- it's
indescribable really.

00:00:31.650 --> 00:00:35.040 align:middle line:84%
For me, I know I have
the skill set to effect

00:00:35.040 --> 00:00:37.170 align:middle line:90%
change in that patient's life.

00:00:37.170 --> 00:00:41.730 align:middle line:84%
But then also to see the
parents and the caregivers so

00:00:41.730 --> 00:00:44.600 align:middle line:90%
appreciative of something that--

00:00:44.600 --> 00:00:45.690 align:middle line:90%
a skill that I have.

00:00:45.690 --> 00:00:48.327 align:middle line:84%
And that I've been able
to make that change.

00:00:48.327 --> 00:00:50.160 align:middle line:84%
